long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
"Rocket League" ⚽🚗

Experience the thrill of soccer with a rocket-powered twist in this exhilarating sports video game developed by Psyonix. "Rocket League" has soared to immense popularity for its unique concept, combining rocket-powered cars with fast-paced gameplay on a giant soccer field. Players control customizable vehicles, aiming to score goals and showcase high-flying acrobatics, blending skill and strategy.

Game Controls 🎮

Mastering the controls is crucial for success in "Rocket League." Here are the basic controls:

Keyboard & Mouse:

W, A, S, D: Drive and steer
Spacebar: Jump
Shift: Boost
Ctrl: Powerslide
Mouse: Camera control
Controller:

Left Stick: Drive and steer
A Button: Jump
B Button: Powerslide
X Button: Boost
Right Stick: Camera control
How to Play ⚙️

Choose Your Car: Select from a variety of customizable rocket-powered cars.

Join a Match: Enter an online match or play offline against AI or local friends.

Score Goals: Use your car’s unique abilities to hit the ball and score goals in the opponent’s net.

Defend Your Goal: Balance offensive and defensive play to prevent the opposing team from scoring.

Master Aerials: Learn to perform aerial maneuvers to gain an edge over opponents. 🚀🏆

Play more games on the top-left menu.
Play on website by clicking on the web version button.
